author: Screen Junkies
description:
We got a chance to ask Zooey Deschanel and Charlie Cox, stars of the upcoming rom-com Merv, all the questions the other outlets were too afraid to ask: does the dog die? How does Merv connect to the MCU? And are there secret messages hidden in the Barenaked Ladies song “one week”?

Voice Narration: Jon Bailey the EPIC VOICE GUY (@epicvoiceguy on all socials)

#honesttrailers #charliecox #zooeydeschanel
title: Honest Trailer Interviews | Charlie Cox & Zooey Deschanel
